{"tid":2130733,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[西餐][意粉迷入] 荔枝角 Pici","createTime":"2020-07-29T11:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T13:07:18.000Z","uid":354871,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a5582e2df5e2504d671d11c5583f63c0bdbf04af","tid":2130733,"uid":354871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:28:33.000Z","msg":"Pici 一直都係我食意粉嘅favourite<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早排有啲想食 點知個on9政府突然停堂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以星期一去完咗心願<br />\n<br />\n雖然間嘢唔平 但食物水準都好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前已經試過灣仔同中環兩間 <br />\n於是試下茘枝角分店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wth2Emq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWth2Emq.jpg&h=862810a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是日menu<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEnevtn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEnevtn.jpg&h=13f4c6b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前菜揀咗Bresaola<br />\nBresaola 係風乾牛肉 用牛小腿加入肉桂等草藥風乾1-3個月<br />\n碟Bresaola幾高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用咗黑白橄欖 橄欖油 小蕃茄 芝士片 <br />\n有油嘅牛食落好滑  同芝士片夾一齊比較正 兩樣味道好strong<br />\n順便帶出芝士鹹香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLwZGz6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLwZGz6.jpg&h=a0c51f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有Cold Cut D火腿同平時唔同 望落勁粉紅 味道比較淡  <br />\n配埋酸瓜酸小洋蔥 幾fresh幾開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身好多食物唔食<br />\n逼住揀Tagliolini Truffle同Lasagna做main<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoimatA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoimatA.jpg&h=4f976f2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先講Lasagna<br />\n用瓷盤兜住白汁焗  冇overcooked冇燶位 但份量偏少<br />\n上菜已經好香<br />\n一食就有一陣濃郁嘅cream香味飄出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過食落冇乜驚喜 一般白汁千層麵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPotzVk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPotzVk.jpg&h=676da1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTagliolini Truffle係松露蛋麵<br />\n嚟到果陣先知係白松露 麵身有D稠 面頭有D芝士碎<br />\n麵條幾彈牙 落咗大量松露油 掛哂係麵條 保持濃厚質感<br />\n由於油感好重 食唔慣多油會唔鐘意<br />\n不過個人幾接受到油膩食物 所以成碟意粉幾啱口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThird course 甜品飲品二揀一 <br />\n見飲品都係coffee or tea <br />\n所以揀咗tiramisu同pinna cotta<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩樣都係奶凍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OicaOfs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOicaOfs.jpg&h=6774e219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTiramisu奶凍 個base唔係咖啡奶凍嚟<br />\n而用咗面頭咖啡粉同最低浸滿哂咖啡嘅蛋糕<br />\n的確帶出expresso濃香 不過食落覺得太苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SpcYW8S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpcYW8S.jpg&h=fd97709d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPinna Cotta 中文叫意式奶凍<br />\n通常淋果醬上面 今次係紅苺醬<br />\n奶味好重 質地係我食過最綿滑嘅甜品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n酸酸嘅紅苺醬平衡咗太甜嘅奶凍<br />\n<br />\n感覺三間分店水準差唔多<br />\n反而唔同季節menu 個體驗落差都幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇上幾次咁啱口味<br />\n<br />\n最後埋單$354 冇加一<br />\n建議大家lunch去食 抵食過夜晚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad8e1491ac0514fd4158e540c49cd17f7d30eb9","tid":2130733,"uid":57827,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"同frd食過灣仔同中環店<br />\n味道超正<br />\n嗌兩個set 竟然包3碟意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa6c6a46d1dfe7d9a4a40dff4f00d85a784eddb","tid":2130733,"uid":18564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:37:59.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀沙田都有分店<br />\n呢間野真係好好食<br />\n堂食先有麵包食 之前係任叫refill <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜外賣唔送埋麵包<br />\n前菜叫coldcuts會有幾種ham&amp;cheese <br />\n唔同口感唔同風味 唔係得個死鹹<br />\n個甜品tiramisu又係好撚好食<br />\n個cream滑到喊 又夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之呢間野係得閒冇事就會想encore既鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9757f034285015ada6300f56309518e72d6f85","tid":2130733,"uid":106326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:30:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1984dc72ff7aa2ce1c8d14b68df73db0463792e","tid":2130733,"uid":22902,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"你呢隻唔係white truffle,係唔靚嘅summer black truffle<br />\n同埋而家出面好多black truffle已經係中國產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好鬼平所以先shave到咁多畀你"},{"pid":"74a16330dd80f8f2b8a8cc2205dedfe915961d35","tid":2130733,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T19:08:12.000Z","msg":"呢間野好食，不過唔知咩集團"},{"pid":"38ebd349626812a71a0a7da6e5b653459e1e7354","tid":2130733,"uid":54194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a16330dd80f8f2b8a8cc2205dedfe915961d35","tid":2130733,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T19:08:12.000Z","msg":"呢間野好食，不過唔知咩集團"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T20:28:25.000Z","msg":"Pirata not sure blue or yellow"},{"pid":"9fa02fcdb53242db6ec6a68966845a15552e706a","tid":2130733,"uid":4813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T21:48:04.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"25285984b1a4417880cbf78b6321b030d1db9433","t